++++-### 7. Numeric formatting
+++++- **Display + Body:** Inter (weights 400, 500, 600, 700, 800), with `font-feature-settings: 'cv11', 'ss01'` for tabular alts and stylistic set
+++++- **Numbers + Labels:** JetBrains Mono (weights 400, 500, 700)
